<h2>Best HVAC Systems for San Diego Climate</h2>

<p>For San Diego's Mediterranean climate, heat pumps with 18+ SEER ratings offer optimal efficiency and versatility. These systems provide both heating and cooling while consuming less energy than traditional split systems. The mild winter temperatures rarely drop below the heat pump's effective operating range, making them ideal year-round solutions. Variable-speed compressors work particularly well in San Diego's moderate climate, adjusting output to match the home's needs rather than cycling on and off frequently.</p>

