<p>Quality contractors offer 24/7 emergency service, crucial during San Diego's occasional heat waves or the rare cold snaps. Request multiple detailed bids that include Manual J load calculations, ensuring proper system sizing for your specific home and microclimate. Check references from recent customers and verify proper insurance coverage, including general liability and workers' compensation. Contractors should also be certified by major manufacturers and familiar with local rebate programs to maximize your savings potential.</p>

